    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade specimen featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies. This unit has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul to ensure peak mechanical synchronicity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, it retains its factory-correct 19-inch forged Style 67 wheels and shows zero evidence of oxidative stress or clear coat failure. A true turn-key enthusiast machine.",
